headline: How Much More Your McDonald’s Big Mac Will Be Due To Trump’s Tariffs on Beef Imports
summary: President Donald Trump has had a uniquely close relationship with the fast food chain McDonald’s. As Business Insider noted in 2017, Trump’s regular order at Mickey D’s is famously a 2,430-calorie combo of two Big Macs, two Fillet-O-Fishes and a large chocolate milkshake. In 2019, the president, when hosting N.C.A.A. football champions the Clemson University Tigers for a White House banquet, rather infamously had the event largely catered by McDonald’s (along with some Burger King and Wendy’s).
